section.section:
The following persons in the order listed may request an accounting of trust property and transactions:
The transferor or the transferor's legal representative;
The beneficiary or the beneficiary's legal representative;
The guardian of the person of the beneficiary;
An adult member of the beneficiary's family or that family member's legal representative; or
A person interested in the trust property or a person interested in the welfare of the beneficiary, either of whom the court determines to have a legitimate interest.
